reviewText:
its a decent video other than having to re edit from pal to dvd american which it was not advertised as pal...
as far as the ninjutsu and other things in it its full of old school acrobatics and stuff that was popular in the old genbukan stuff..
the whole if you can do ukemi you can do ninjutsyu theme is definitely rampant here.
like i said old skool stuff. it has a few treasures but again don't know if its worth it
good but nothing here will make you wanna run out and buy it atleast not unless the price was right.
